{
  "stem": "12455.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I cut my hair almost every week with the clippers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had one of the farmers do that for me before it grew up-- it grew out and extended where it started curling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it wasn't noticeable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where I got all that knowledge as a kid to do all these things, I had the slightest-- I don't have the slightest idea.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I say, something was guiding me and telling me what to do and how to do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what I did until 1944 when the-- that night-- that day when the Germans was-- were retreating, I went in-- in a-- in a field.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the lady that I stayed with, she had a sister that lived-- she had a shack in the field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She lived with her husband and two children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I came to her after I ran away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And  she told me that since everybody is dead and the houses burned down, I could stay with her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stayed with her for a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then word came that the Russians are in the village, which means that the town near the village was liberated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got up one morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was scared to tell them where I was going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was scared to tell him I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I just got up one morning, and I left and didn't say nothing to anybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I left, I went on the main road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Summer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got on the main road, and I was walking towards Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "O-S-T-R-O-G.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at times-- at time-- at times, it was Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But at the time during the war, it belonged to Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
